These are Puzzles for 6x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-1::.
There 3 different types of food: grapefruit, garlic, pepper
The people have 3 different jobs:  scientist, social-worker, mechanic
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: salsa, funk, punk
3 different pets are kept: frog, guinea-pig, horse
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: water-polo, lacrosse, volleyball
The people use 3 different means of transport: motorbike, tram, quad-bike
 1. the person eating garlic is on the left or right of the person eating pepper##3
 2. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##3
 3. the social-worker is on the right of the fan of punk##1
 4. the person eating garlic is the fan of funk##1
 5. the owner of the frog is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 6. the social-worker is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the scientist is the person eating grapefruit##1
 8. the person driving the motorbike is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 9. the person eating pepper is between the owner of the guinea-pig and the person driving the quad-bike##2
10. the person driving the motorbike is in an odd position##4
11. the scientist is the owner of the horse##1
12. the mechanic is the person driving the tram##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |         2          |     3      |
| Food          | grapefruit   | pepper            | garlic     |
| Job           | scientist | mechanic | social-worker |
| Music-Genre   | salsa      | punk               | funk        |
| Pet           | horse        | frog         | guinea-pig   |
| Sport         | volleyball     | lacrosse      | water-polo       |
| Transport     | quad-bike        | tram              | motorbike       |

