.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, fanta, coffee
There 3 different types of food: cucumber, garlic, cherry
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: martial-arts, romance, western
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: dubstep, punk, soul
3 different pets are kept: bird, ferret, cat
The people use 3 different means of transport: roller, snowmobile, ship
 1. the person eating cucumber is the person watching western movies##1
 2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
 3. the fan of punk is in an odd position##4
 4. the person eating cherry is the fan of dubstep##1
 5. the person driving the ship is between the person eating cucumber and the person watching martial-arts movies##2
 6. the owner of the bird is between the person eating garlic and the person driving the roller##2
 7. the person drinking coffee is the owner of the ferret##1
 8. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the person eating cherry##1
 9. the person eating garlic is on the far left or far right##3
10. the fan of soul is the person watching martial-arts movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |      3      |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | fanta | coffee        |
| Food          | garlic   | cherry    | cucumber        |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts    | romance | western |
| Music-Genre   | soul   | dubstep  | punk         |
| Pet           | cat    | bird | ferret       |
| Transport     | snowmobile   | ship    | roller  |

