.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, soy-milk, lemonade
There 3 different types of food: pineapple, grapes, pear
The people have 3 different hobbies: filmmaking, camping, skydiving
The people have 3 different jobs:  nurse, analyst, police-officer
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: zombie, musical, scientific
3 different pets are kept: horse, rabbit, goldfish
 1. the nurse is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
 2. the police-officer is the person eating pear##1
 3. the person watching musical movies is the person drinking soy-milk##1
 4. the owner of the horse is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the person eating pineapple is between the person who's hobby is camping and the owner of the rabbit##2
 6. the person eating pear is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
 7. the person drinking soy-milk is in an odd position##4
 8. the person watching musical movies is on the left or right of the person watching scientific movies##3
 9. the police-officer is on the far right##1
10. the person who's hobby is skydiving is in an odd position##4
11. the person who's hobby is camping is the analyst##1
12. the person watching musical movies is on the far left##1
13. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left or right of the owner of the rabbit##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |      3       |
| Beverage      | soy-milk        | cola     | lemonade          |
| Food          | grapes     | pineapple | pear    |
| Hobby         | camping    | filmmaking  | skydiving |
| Job           | analyst | nurse    | police-officer    |
| Movie-Genre   | musical      | scientific | zombie      |
| Pet           | horse          | goldfish     | rabbit         |

