The people prefer 3 different music-genres: funk, classical, country
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, thai, indonesian
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rugby, rowing, swimming
 1. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
 2. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 3. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
 4. the fan of country is on the far right##1
 5. the fan of funk is between the person who's sport is rowing and the person who's hobby is writing##2
 6. the thai is on the far right##1
 7. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
 8. the person watching scientific movies is the person who's sport is rugby##1
 9. the canadian is in an odd position##4
10. the indonesian is in an even position##4
11. the thai is on the far left or far right##3
12. the person who's hobby is writing is the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3       |
| Beverage      | tea  | soy-milk      | lemonade        |
| Hobby         | writing   | singing     | board-games |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | comedy | animation     |
| Music-Genre   | classical    | funk         | country         |
| Nationality   | canadian   | indonesian     | thai      |
| Sport         | rugby  | swimming     | rowing         |

