.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-18::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, soy-milk, hot-chocolate
The people have 3 different hobbies: dancing, magic-tricks, collecting
The people have 3 different jobs:  entrepreneur, pilot, firefighter
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, reggae, house
There are 3 different nationalities: mexican, french, egyptian
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, sailing, swimming
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the egyptian##1
2. the fan of reggae is between the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the egyptian##2
3. the mexican is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left or right of the fan of blues##3
5. the person who's sport is sailing is on the far left##1
6. the pilot is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
7. the fan of blues is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
8. the person who's sport is badminton is between the entrepreneur and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
9. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |         2          |      3      |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate    | soy-milk           | almond-milk         |
| Hobby         | collecting   | dancing             | magic-tricks  |
| Job           | firefighter  | pilot | entrepreneur |
| Music-Genre   | blues      | reggae              | house      |
| Nationality   | egyptian | french             | mexican     |
| Sport         | sailing   | badminton           | swimming      |

