.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-19::.
There 3 different types of food: cauliflower, pomegranate, banana
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, blues, jazz
There are 3 different nationalities: russian, indian, malaysian
3 different pets are kept: ferret, hamster, fish
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: volleyball, basketball, rugby
The people use 3 different means of transport: jet-ski, helicopter, trike
 1. the russian is in an odd position##4
 2. the person eating banana is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
 3. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 4. the owner of the hamster is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3
 5. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the fan of blues##1
 6. the person driving the trike is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
 7. the owner of the hamster is on the far left##1
 8. the malaysian is on the right of the fan of ambient##1
 9. the fan of blues is the person eating pomegranate##1
10. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |    3    |
| Food          | pomegranate    | banana  | cauliflower   |
| Music-Genre   | blues      | ambient  | jazz  |
| Nationality   | russian | indian  | malaysian |
| Pet           | hamster     | ferret   | fish   |
| Sport         | volleyball  | basketball | rugby |
| Transport     | trike   | jet-ski      | helicopter  |

