.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-20::.
There 3 different types of food: apricot, grapefruit, peas
The people have 3 different hobbies: hiking, rock-climbing, dancing
The people have 3 different jobs:  paramedic, coach, analyst
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: satire, thriller, horror
There are 3 different nationalities: italian, spanish, british
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: weightlifting, surfing, parkour
 1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the person who's sport is parkour##1
 2. the person eating peas is on the right of the person eating grapefruit##1
 3. the person watching horror movies is the person eating apricot##1
 4. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
 5. the person who's hobby is hiking is in an even position##4
 6. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the analyst is on the left of the person eating apricot##1
 8. the paramedic is on the left or right of the italian##3
 9. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the coach##1
10. the coach is the spanish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2       |     3      |
| Food          | grapefruit     | peas   | apricot     |
| Hobby         | dancing | hiking   | rock-climbing  |
| Job           | paramedic   | analyst | coach   |
| Movie-Genre   | satire    | thriller       | horror    |
| Nationality   | british        | italian    | spanish   |
| Sport         | surfing      | weightlifting     | parkour |

 